    <refsect1 xml:id="description"><title>Description</title>
        <para>
            <function>min</function> returns the minimum of the two parameters. It
            returns <parameter>y</parameter> if <parameter>y</parameter> is less than
            <parameter>x</parameter>, otherwise it returns <parameter>x</parameter>.
        </para>
